ed="T" n="0775b08"/><persName key="A010501">釋曇晟</persName>，俗姓<name>王</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000018931"><placeName>鍾陵</placeName><placeName>建昌</placeName></placeName>人也。始生有自<lb
ed="T" n="0775b09"/>然胎衣右袒，猶緇服焉。遂請出家於<placeName key="PL000000018910">石門</placeName><ptr target="#n1558"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0775b10"/>年滿具法，參見<placeName key="PL000000019628">百丈山</placeName><persName key="A001897">海<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>。二十年為<lb
ed="T" n="0775b11"/>侍者，職同<persName key="A003861">慶喜</persName>，法必我聞，身若中涓<ptr type="glossary" target="#g932"/>，心居<lb
ed="T" n="0775b12"/>散位<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1564"/>。續受<persName key="A010510">藥山</persName>舉發，全了無疑，化徒孔勤，<lb
ed="T" n="0775b13"/>受益者眾。以<date key="j20241812024181" when-iso="+0829-12-01"><name><anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz6"/>太<anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz6"/>和</name>三年<anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz7"/>己<anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz7"/>酉十月二十七日</date><lb
ed="T" n="0775b14"/>示滅<ptr target="#n1559"/>。勅謚<anchor xml:id="beg0775006"/>大<anchor xml:id="end0775006"/>師號<persName key="A010501">無相</persName><ptr target="#n1560"/>，塔名<placeName key="PL000000057006">淨勝</placeName>焉。</p><p><lb
ed="T" n="0775b15"/>系曰：<persName key="A008803">商那和脩</persName>，<name>華</name>言<persName key="A008803">胎衣</persName>也，以其生帶衣<lb
ed="T" n="0775b16"/>而誕，<anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz8"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>以</sic><corr>似</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz8"/>繒肉而非，幼為繃<anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz9"/>褓<anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz9"/>，長且稱身；出<lb
ed="T" n="0775b17"/>家成法服，至入滅闍維，方為煨燼焉。<persName key="A010501">晟<roleName>師</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0775b18"/>之有胎衣，止不及為嬰兒已往之服耳，此<lb
ed="T" n="0775b19"/>近<persName key="A017110">叔離尼</persName><ptr target="#n2652"/>、<persName key="A008803">商那尊者</persName>也，思過半<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1565"/>矣。何邪？<persName key="A010501">晟<lb
ed="T" n="0775b20"/><roleName>師</roleName></persName>去聖懸遠，<persName key="A008803">和修</persName>佛滅百年將胎衣示有<lb
ed="T" n="0775b21"/>行果之徒也，今<persName key="A010501">晟</persName>以胞<anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz10"/>袒<anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz10"/>絡化其教理之<lb
ed="T" n="0775b22"/>世，不其難乎！故曰思<anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz11"/>過<anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz11"/>半矣。</p>
